reviewText:
I'm a Vietnam Vet  who has been back through Vietnam a couple of times, Cambodia and  Thailand and Laos.

The people have been very welcoming and the countries are beautiful without war going one and one can finally enjoy visiting and interacting with the people.

Could have been done better but I did like the attempt it made to deal with this topic.
Would love to see China Beach on my Kindle with Dana Delany if you know what I mean.
